- score_breakdown: { urgence, budget, accessibilite, concurrence, proximite, historique }

Donnees brutes du prospect:
${raw}

Contexte marche local:
${context}

Reponds UNIQUEMENT en JSON.`;
  }

  if (sector === 'coaching') {
    return `Tu es un expert en developpement commercial pour coachs professionnels. Analyse ce signal et genere un JSON:
- score (0-100, urgence transition, budget coaching, accessibilite contact, concurrence)
